## Update Procedure

When making updates:
1. Edit OPENCLAW_DOCUMENTATION.md
2. Add entry to this log
3. Increment version (V1.0 → V1.1)
4. Git commit with message: "docs: [TYPE] - [DESCRIPTION]"
5. Git push to main branch

